@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram - Ott Based System Mini Reel

[*] --> Start

state "Start" as Start
state "Account Created" as AccountCreated
state "Watching Video" as WatchingVideo
state "Uploaded Video" as UploadedVideo
state "Liked Video" as LikedVideo
state "Viewing Likes" as ViewingLikes
state "Discussing" as Discussing
state "End" as End

Start --> AccountCreated : Create Account

AccountCreated --> WatchingVideo : Watch Video

WatchingVideo --> UploadedVideo : Upload Video
WatchingVideo --> LikedVideo : Save to Likes
WatchingVideo --> Discussing : Enter Discussion

UploadedVideo --> WatchingVideo : Back to Watching

LikedVideo --> ViewingLikes : View Likes

ViewingLikes --> WatchingVideo : Back to Watching
ViewingLikes --> End : Finish

Discussing --> End : Finish

[*] <-- End

@enduml
